Ecommerce Arena â€“ Refund, Return & Cancellation Policy 
At Ecommerce Arena, transparency and customer satisfaction are at the core of our operations.

ï‚· The service has not been fully delivered or completed. 
ï‚· For subscription-based services, less than 30% usage of allocated monthly limits has 
occurred. 
ï‚· The customer can clearly describe the issue or dissatisfaction with the service. 
Refunds are not applicable if: 
ï‚· The work has already been delivered as per the agreed scope.

ï‚· Delays occurred due to missing information from the customer. 
ï‚· The customer changed their business requirements after delivery started.

ï‚· Additional custom work had already been initiated.

3. Non-Refundable Services

ï‚· Product photography or media editing once files have been delivered

ï‚· Any service involving third-party payment (API, automation credits, etc.)

ï‚· Via email to support@ecommercearena.com 
ï‚· At least 48 hours before the next billing cycle 
Service access remains valid until the end of the billing period.
